Publish Tableau Content to CRM Analytics

Easily publish Tableau Cloud and Tableau Server dashboards, sheets, and stories to a CRM Analytics app or Lightning page without first embedding Tableau views or installing additional software.

To use this feature, Enable Publishing Tableau Views.
Select the view that you want to publish to CRM Analytics from Tableau Cloud or Tableau Server.
Click Connect to Salesforce and specify the Salesforce credentials that you want to use for publishing.
In the Publish to Salesforce dialog box, select the destination app that you want to publish the Tableau view to, and then click Publish.

You can save, favorite, delete, or remove a published view from its action menu.
title: Publishing Tableau Content to Salesforce
